item.description:
Please join me for some fun and exercise while we toss discs along the wooded paths at Muldoon park. Please meet me across the street at Hillside General Store to grab water and free loaner discs. If you have your own, feel free to bring them too.  You don't have to be good at tossing a frisbee, just come out and give it a try. We don't judge,we just have fun.

Please wear good shoes , bring water, bug spray and what ever you may need to wander thru the woods. We can stop back at the store for sandwiches after were dun if anyone wants.

Here is a link for more info and directions to the park.

http://www.dgcoursereview.com/course.php?id=4935

 

Info, lost ? 603-315-0275

**Rain will cancel this event **

 

Please only YES rsvps and a face picture to help us meet for the event..Thank you
item.how_to_find_us: we'll meet at the store across from the park to pick up discs
